# WebRTC Video Recording

This project demonstrates how to record videos using WebRTC. It supports starting, stopping, pausing, resuming, and resetting recordings. The project also includes functionality for uploading videos, with support for background sync to handle unreliable internet connections, and saving video URLs to IndexedDB.

## Features

- Record video from the webcam
- Start, stop, pause, resume, and reset recordings
- Upload videos using background sync if the internet is unreliable
- Save video URLs to IndexedDB

